xrestop: xrestop
xrestop: 
xrestop: Xrestop uses the X-Resource extension to provide 'top' like statistics
xrestop: of each connected X11 client's server side resource usage. 
xrestop: It is intended as a developer tool to aid more efficient server resource usage
xrestop: and debug server side leakage. 
xrestop: It should work with any server supporting the X-Resource extension,
xrestop: including the Xorg server and XFree86 4.3+.
xrestop:
xrestop: https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/xrestop/
xrestop:
